Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118550,121440}We want to repay you for the last time.{NOTE:それはこの前のを返しをさせてもらうことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121440,122460}What's that?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122460,123950}Quit dreaming.{NOTE:強がりを止しなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123950,125980}Nothing's going to change.{NOTE:いくらやっても、同じこと。}
