Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138740,141160}Hey, April Fools is long over.{NOTE:ね、エープリルフールは過ぎたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142240,145430}Just to make it clear: we've already proved our skill before.{NOTE:言っとくけどさ、この前実力で勝ったんですからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145430,146210}Got it?{NOTE:お分かり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147080,149210}That's why we want to repay you with skill.{NOTE:だから実力XXX返しようと言うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149210,149710}Got it?{NOTE:分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150080,153600}We won't let you keep that boastful attitude forever. Got it?{NOTE:あなたたちにね…何時までも大きな顔させないてこと。分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153600,154390}We get it.{NOTE:よく分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155060,158470}Looks like the last time wasn't enough for you after all.{NOTE:どうやら、もう一度可愛がるほか成せそうだわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158470,159090}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159820,164250}That's ridiculous. Our Big Four is\htoo\hgood to accept such a request.{NOTE:馬鹿馬鹿しいじゃん。四天王XXXこんな(XXX・練習試合)にするなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164250,167360}No trash talk. We'll play with them all right.{NOTE:だからさ。ぐうの音もでないようにしてやるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167360,168280}Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168280,169910}We'll play with the same people.{NOTE:ファイト同じメンバーでいいのね。}
