Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187510,191970}You've taken place of our professor Kajioka as the new coach to promote yourself, no?{NOTE:あたしたちの梶岡先生下ろして、コーチに売り込んだ。そういうつもりなんでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191970,194190}Whoa.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195940,197140}What are you saying?{NOTE:なに言ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197140,199880}Professor Hongou is not like that.{NOTE:そんな本郷先生じゃないのよ。}
