Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211130,212240}I won't forgive it.{NOTE:許せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212240,214760}As the club members, for you to cast us out…{NOTE:バレー部員としてあたしたちを除け者にしようなんて…}
