Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218260,219080}Professor!{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219080,221100}How about you say something?{NOTE:何とか言ったらどうなんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221100,222790}That's right. Professor Hongou.{NOTE:そうよ。本郷先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222790,225130}She's yelling so much.{NOTE:こんな人怒鳴りつけて…}
