Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248550,249300}That's correct.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249300,250030}We did.{NOTE:言いました。}
