Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585750,589130}After telling Izumi-san, let's put our resignation together tomorrow.{NOTE:泉さんに話して、明日は四人一緒に退部届けよう。}
