Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590130,592430}Who'd want to be in that club anyway.{NOTE:誰があんなバレー部いてやるもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593380,594720}Keep it straight!{NOTE:(XXX・黄線)だ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601700,602460}Fight, fight!{NOTE:ファイト、ファイト！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602460,603460}Don't space out!{NOTE:ぼやぼやするな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603460,605090}Watch the ball closely!{NOTE:良く玉を見ろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615970,617530}No matter what professor said…{NOTE:先生あんなこと言うけど、}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617530,618680}It's no use.{NOTE:無理よね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618680,620050}What is?{NOTE:無理って？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620050,622430}The Big Four are sure to quit the club now.{NOTE:四天王きっと止めちゃうわ、バレー部を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622430,624810}We can't let them do that.{NOTE:やめさせるわけにはいかないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625660,629100}Our power will fall considerably.{NOTE:あたしたち先じゃ大変な戦力低下よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629100,630520}That's weak, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:弱気な、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630520,633390}Even without the Big Four we're plenty capable on our own.{NOTE:四天王なんかいなくだって、あたしたちって十分やっていけるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633390,635660}Ah, I wonder about that.{NOTE:あ、それはどうかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635660,638190}Izumi-san acted strange today.{NOTE:今の泉さん何とか変だもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638190,640320}I can't believe she gave it all she had.{NOTE:あれは実力と思えないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640320,643200}At any rate, I'll try talking to them tomorrow again.{NOTE:とにかく、明日もう一度話してみるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643200,644270}It's useless.{NOTE:無駄よ、無駄。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644270,646640}I'm positive they'll drop out.{NOTE:退部直ぐに決まってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647020,649420}I absolutely won't let them do that.{NOTE:んん。絶対に退部させないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649420,651340}– You're so stubborn.\N– Same goes to you.{NOTE:—強情ね。\\N—あなたこそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651340,652650}Hehe.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653120,654440}I'm trying to be a realist.{NOTE:いいや、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654440,656330}I'll leave it to you, captain.{NOTE:キャプテンにお任せするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.55,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658240,659550}I'll take my chances.{NOTE:やってみる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659550,662350}I'll show you that I can persuade the Big Four.{NOTE:あたしの力で四天王を説得してみせる。}
Comment: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:05.58,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:665581,665581}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665710,669060}{\1c&H141414&\3c&H141414&\t(0,1500,\1c&H9AFBDC&\3c&H202020&)}Club resignation letter{NOTE:退部届}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668300,669060}Ah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669580,673290}Well then, now that we have our letters ready…{NOTE:さ、それで三人の退部届は揃ったわけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673290,674220}Where's Izumi-san?{NOTE:ね、泉さんは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674220,676540}Seems like she's absent today.{NOTE:それはさ、お休みらしいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677990,680820}I thought we'd deliver the letters with all four of us.{NOTE:どうせ、退部届らすなら四人に一緒にと思ったのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681400,683410}I wonder what happened to Izumi-san.{NOTE:一体どうしたかしら、泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683410,685310}Yesterdays game must've gotten to her.{NOTE:昨日のショックは大きいなのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685310,685980}Surely.{NOTE:きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685810,688750}Izumi family{NOTE:泉}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690360,691580}No.{NOTE:いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691920,692740}Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692740,693710}By "no" I mean "no".{NOTE:いやったら、いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693710,696570}I don't want to go to the hospital again.{NOTE:大の病院なんかいつもんですか、絶対いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696570,698730}But it looks very painful.{NOTE:だって、とても痛そうじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698730,700950}Playing more with that arm is reckless.{NOTE:その腕で試合をするなんて無茶ですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700950,701750}Right?{NOTE:ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702760,703930}Let's go.{NOTE:さ、早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703930,706430}I'll go with you, okay?{NOTE:お母さんも一緒に来ますから。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708330,710660}If you want to go that much, then go without me.{NOTE:そんなに行きたきゃ、お母さん一人で行けば良いじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710660,713060}I'm not going there.{NOTE:あたしはいやよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713060,714290}Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714290,715640}Hold on!{NOTE:お待ちに…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716530,717570}Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729400,731650}So, do you think you'll be able to persuade them?{NOTE:で、君には説得する自身があるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731650,733890}Hm. To be honest, I'm not really sure.{NOTE:んん。それで実は困ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733890,736070}Hey, maybe you can think of something?{NOTE:ね、何か良い考えないかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736070,738280}I said that in the heat of the moment yesterday…{NOTE:昨日は弾みであんなこと言っちゃったけど、}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738280,742710}…but I honestly don't think I can make friends with these girls.{NOTE:正直などこはあの人達と仲良くする何てできそうにないんもね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742710,747590}But both you and the Big Four share the love for volleyball, don't you.{NOTE:だけど、君達だって、四天王だって…バレーを愛することに軽いはないんだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747590,749250}Of course we do.{NOTE:それはもちろんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749250,752090}Why can't you join forces then?{NOTE:それだったらさ…なぜチームが組めれないんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752090,755210}I can't help but think you've misunderstood each other.{NOTE:君達のどっかに誤解なるとしか考えられないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755210,757860}In this world there are things that even bugs won't touch.{NOTE:世の中には虫が付かないってこともあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757860,758790}Hehe.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758790,761410}You can be harsh at times, you know.{NOTE:大体、君は頭にXXXだからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761410,762350}Hm.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764030,769210}I just remembered how you almost got in a fight with Hayakawa-san in the past.{NOTE:それに、早川くんの時だって、殴り合い寸前に成ったそうじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769210,770740}Ah, you knew it?{NOTE:あ、いやだ、知ってたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770740,772460}That's a newspaper club member for you.{NOTE:さすが新聞部は早耳ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772460,773230}Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773230,775040}Ah, you girls.{NOTE:あ、あなたたち…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775040,776040}Huh.{NOTE:は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783910,784800}Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784800,786670}– Sorry for all the trouble.\N– Eh?{NOTE:—色々お世話になりました。\\N—へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787220,790070}– We're quitting the volleyball club.\N– Oh, my.{NOTE:—あたしたちはバレー部を辞めるの。\\N—ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790070,792080}See for yourself.{NOTE:ほら、この通り見てよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792080,794900}It's a resignation letter.\NWe're on the way to professor Hongou.{NOTE:退部届よ。今本郷先生に持ってく途中。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794900,796150}That's too bad.{NOTE:そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796150,800960}Girls, haven't you staked everything on volleyball so far? And yet…{NOTE:あなたたち、バレーに命をかけていたじゃないの。それなのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801610,803930}"Staked everything"? Don't be absurd.{NOTE:命をかけた？ご冗談でしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803930,805310}It's just a stupid ball game.{NOTE:あんなボール遊び何か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805310,806430}You're not serious!{NOTE:嘘！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806430,808090}I understand you more than you think.{NOTE:あたしには分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808090,810760}There's no way you're thinking that for real.{NOTE:あなた方は嘘を付いてるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810760,812770}I'm a fool for volleyball myself, so I know it.{NOTE:バレーバカに成ったあたしだから分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812770,816430}But you can only play well if you are serious about it.{NOTE:遊び半分の練習で、あなたたちほどの実力は付く分けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816430,817680}Don't you see it?{NOTE:そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817680,822140}Fufufu. So you stopped us just to boast how good you are?{NOTE:フフフ。その実力者を破ったXXXは、天才だとでも言いたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822140,823270}What do you mean?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823270,824100}All right, let's go.{NOTE:さ、行きましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824100,825450}Hold on!{NOTE:待って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825450,827330}Don't be stubborn. Please?{NOTE:意地を張るのは止して。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827330,829190}– Please think it ove—\N– We've had enough.{NOTE:—よく考えて…\\N—XXXたくさんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829190,830980}Let's go, let's go.{NOTE:—行こう、行こう。\\N—行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837800,839940}Is it okay to let them go like that?{NOTE:このままでしておいて良いのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843680,844870}Wait, wait!{NOTE:待って！待って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844870,846850}What now?{NOTE:な、何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847970,848690}Wh—!{NOTE:な…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848690,850770}What are you doing!{NOTE:何するのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852600,854970}Hey, give it back!{NOTE:—ちょっと返してよ！\\N—返してよ！待ちな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854970,856210}Give it back!{NOTE:返してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856210,858350}Get over here!{NOTE:早く返してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858710,862020}Oh, I didn't know Ayuhara-san can handle paperwork well.{NOTE:へ。鮎原くんは掻っ払いXXXしらなかったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862020,863810}{\fad(0,500)}Class 3C{NOTE:３年c組}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863810,866780}What a way to make a person look like a fool.{NOTE:まったく人をバカにしてやりかたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866780,868910}We can't let her off the hook like that.{NOTE:このまま放っとくてはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868910,871500}If you don't do something, I will.{NOTE:あんたたちやらなきゃ、あたしだけでもやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872890,874880}Yeah. I won't be staying silent.{NOTE:そうよ。黙ってられもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874880,876300}Katori-san. What about you?{NOTE:香取さん。あんたは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876300,878920}W-Well, same goes for me.{NOTE:そ…それは、あたしだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879350,880070}All right.{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880070,881240}Let's call her over somewhere.{NOTE:どっか呼び出そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881240,883490}How about near the river?{NOTE:富士見川の川原なんかどう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883490,885570}Sounds good. I'll go.{NOTE:良いわ。あたしはそう行ってくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886970,887820}Ah, it's you.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887820,889120}Good timing.{NOTE:ちょうどよかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889120,893260}Kudou-san. I want to talk to you.{NOTE:工藤さん。あなたたちにちょっと話があるんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893260,894510}– Talk?\N– Yep.{NOTE:—話？\\N—え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894510,896990}Come to see me by the riverbank after classes.{NOTE:授業が終わったら、富士見川の川原来て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896990,899410}I'll be waiting. It's a promise!{NOTE:待ってるわ。きっとよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899410,900880}Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903170,905040}Damn it, she played me like a fiddle.{NOTE:臭う、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925310,926850}We're here.{NOTE:XXX}
