Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944730,946950}Never mind the others and focus on Ayuhara.{NOTE:他の人は良いから、鮎原だけをマークして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946950,948010}Got it?{NOTE:良いわね。}
