Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960620,961810}Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962630,964010}You're late.{NOTE:遅かったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968000,969020}Are you alone?{NOTE:あんた、一人？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969020,970900}Yes. Why are you asking?{NOTE:そうよ。なぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970900,972900}Then why have you called us here?{NOTE:じゃ、どうしたあたしたちを呼び出したのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973550,975350}There's something I wanted to ask you.{NOTE:聞きたいことがあっただから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975600,976610}It's about this.{NOTE:これよ。}
