Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978650,979800}Let's hear whatever it is.{NOTE:言ってごらんなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979800,982360}Do you really want to quit the volleyball club?{NOTE:あなたたちは本当にバレー部を辞めるつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982360,985570}Of course we do. Why do you keep bothering us?{NOTE:ん。もちろんよ。当たり前じゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985570,987860}I may have fought with you until now.{NOTE:あたしはあなたたちと争ってだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987860,990340}But I have always respected your talent.{NOTE:でもあなたたちの力を尊敬していたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990340,991270}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991630,992370}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992370,995980}I respect your serve and spike too, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あたくしだも鮎原さんのサーブとスパイクを尊敬しておりますのよ。}
