Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996820,1001510}If we join our forces, we might make an excellent team together.{NOTE:そのあたしとあなたたちは力を合わせたら、すごいチームに成ると思うけどな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001510,1003090}Eh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003860,1005560}Are you serious about that?{NOTE:本気でそう思ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005560,1006660}Certainly.{NOTE:もちろん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006660,1009340}We're in the same club and I want to win matches.{NOTE:だって、同じバレーをやりからには、試合に勝ちたいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009340,1012570}Don't you want to make a strong team even a little bit?{NOTE:少しでも…少しでも強いチームを作りたいでしょう?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012570,1014660}We're in the same club?{NOTE:同じバレーをやるからには？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014660,1015760}Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016330,1018060}Too bad.{NOTE:お生憎様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018570,1022210}We don't want to see a volleyball ever again.{NOTE:あたしたち…二度とバレーボールを見るXXいやよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022210,1024310}So you're dropping out no matter what?{NOTE:じゃ、どうしても退部届よ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024310,1025270}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025270,1027150}Hand over the letters.{NOTE:返してよ、退部届。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029800,1032300}No matter how much you disturb us, I'm quitting.{NOTE:あんたはいくらじゃましたって、あたしたちは辞めるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034360,1036340}To hell with volleyball.{NOTE:バレーボールなんか糞XXXだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036340,1037430}Give it back!{NOTE:返してよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038890,1040240}Give it back.{NOTE:—返して。\\N—返して。\\N—返して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040240,1042020}Give it back!{NOTE:—返すのよ。\\N—返すのよ。\\N—返すのよ。}
