Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052520,1053190}Ah…{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053190,1056940}If you hate volleyball that much, let's see you cut up that ball.{NOTE:そんなにバレーが憎いなら、こうしてボールを裂いてごらんなさい。}
