Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117590,1119370}It's crying.{NOTE:泣いてるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119370,1121750}Until yesterday, that ball was your true friend.{NOTE:ボールは昨日まであなたの親友だったのね。}
