Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172480,1174730}You can't quit volleyball.{NOTE:あなたたちはバレーを辞めちゃいけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176470,1178880}Since your love for volleyball is true…{NOTE:XXバレーを愛してるのが本当なら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178880,1180900}Why do we even fight?{NOTE:なぜあたしたちはいがみ合ってるの？}
