Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235940,1239880}Shouldn't they come to us bowing their heads by now?{NOTE:でもさ、今さらあんな連中にペコペコすることないじゃん？}
