Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309230,1312980}I can't blame her. Izumi-san's mom is actually her stepmother after all.{NOTE:無理ないわよ。泉さんの母さんて継母だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312980,1314240}A stepmother…{NOTE:継母…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314240,1317000}We'll tell her later. I'm sure she'll understand.{NOTE:後で行きます。きっと泉さんも分かってくれるわよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317000,1319830}I wonder if it goes well. She can be scary at times.{NOTE:うまく行くかな？彼女(XXX・無意義何と怖さら)ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319830,1320480}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320480,1323420}Without Izumi-san, the name of Big Four loses its sense.{NOTE:泉くんはいないと、四天王の意味はなくなるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323420,1324750}That's right.{NOTE:その通りだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324750,1327330}Professor. I'll go check on her and visit her home.{NOTE:先生。泉さんの家にあたしは行ってみます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327330,1329380}All right, professor?{NOTE:ね、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329380,1330110}Hm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330110,1332440}Ah. Let us go too then.{NOTE:あら、じゃ、あたしたちも一緒に行きましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333010,1335070}You should focus on practice.{NOTE:あなたたちは練習、練習。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335070,1336510}I'll be fine by myself.{NOTE:あたし一人で大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337300,1340010}Very well. Let's leave it to Ayuhara.{NOTE:よし。じゃ、鮎原に行ってもらおう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340010,1341210}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341210,1343390}{\fad(0,1000)}Izumi family{NOTE:泉}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347990,1349840}What a mansion.{NOTE:大したお屋敷ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350750,1351970}Excuse me.{NOTE:ごめんください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352360,1353830}Excuse me.{NOTE:ごめんください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354670,1355850}I wonder if they're out.{NOTE:お留守かしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355850,1357440}Who might you be?{NOTE:どなた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357440,1360070}Ah. I beg your pardon, is Izumi Yuri-san home?{NOTE:あ、あの…泉ゆりさんいらっしゃいます？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360070,1362410}Ah, you're Yuri's friend?{NOTE:あ、ゆりのお友達？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362410,1364240}Yes, ma'am. My name's Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:はい。鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365420,1367340}Ah, nice to meet you. Welcome.{NOTE:あ、そうですか。どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368950,1371900}Yuri will be home soon. Make yourself comfortable.{NOTE:ゆりもう直ぐXXX。どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371900,1373120}Excuse me.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375250,1375790}However…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376410,1376960}Hm?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1378220,1380950}You're not a member of the volleyball club by any chance, are you?{NOTE:あなた、バレー部の方じゃありませんわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380950,1383380}Spot on. I am its member.{NOTE:当たりました。そのバレー部なんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1384300,1385720}I am very sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385720,1388340}I'm afraid I can't let you see Yuri.{NOTE:バレー部の方にはいただけないんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388340,1389020}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389720,1394180}I'm sorry for troubling you with this request only now, but could you please go home?{NOTE:わざわざで来ましたも悪いんですけど、このまま帰っていただきません？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394180,1400480}Ah, why is that? I came here out of the blue, but I'd rather not go home until I meet with Yuri.{NOTE:あ、なぜですか？あたし薮から棒にそんなこと言われても、あたし帰るわけにはいきません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1402400,1403640}Why?{NOTE:なぜですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1403640,1404870}Shut up and go home.{NOTE:黙って帰って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407840,1409190}Ah, Izumi-san.{NOTE:あ、泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409190,1410350}Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1410350,1411780}Go home.{NOTE:帰ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411780,1413460}You're not welcome here.{NOTE:ここはあんたのXXX所じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413460,1414570}Hurry.{NOTE:早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416530,1417620}Get out!{NOTE:帰ってたら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.69,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421320,1422690}Why?{NOTE:なぜ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.12,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422690,1424120}What's going on?{NOTE:一体なぜなの？}
