Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:16.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452670,1456860}But seeing Yuri's attitude, her hand reacts instinctively.{NOTE:こんな態度に、こずえは思わずゆりの方に手は飛んだ。}
